data.description: 435 N Allen St is a modern farmhouse and has a classic look of white walls and black accents throughout.  Large, open concept kitchen and living room combo.  Kitchen boasts a 9' Long Island that seats 6 and a deep farmhouse sink.  An oversized hidden pantry and plenty of cabinets provide ample storage.  Luxury vinyl plank flooring and carpet throughout.  The second floor includes 4 bedrooms, and 2.5 baths.  Lots of extra touches including a mud room/drop zone, laundry room with utility sink, covered deck, fenced back yard, a five zone sprinkler system and built in speakers throughout the home.  There is a finished basement with full bath, and a bar.  A 3-stall garage provides extra storage and parking.  Less than 1.5 miles from Bennington High/Middle Schools and Bennington Elementary is walkable.
